snippet.title: REVOLVER
snippet.description: Revolver is North America’s leading hard-rock and metal media brand. In print for over 18 years, the magazine has provided its readers with unmatched access to the biggest bands in heavy music as well as the scene’s most important up-and-comers. Revolver recently underwent a massive brand relaunch, complete with a radically redesigned print edition and website that embody the art and culture of heavy music.
